  let P1 Оө2 n := {(в„° n (ПҒвҠ—^S[n])).M вүҘвӮҡ (Real.exp (вҶ‘n*((R1 ПҒ Оө).toReal + Оө2))) вҖў (Пғ'' ПҒ Оө m Пғ n).M}
  let P2 Оө2 n := {(в„° n (ПҒвҠ—^S[n])).M вүҘвӮҡ (Real.exp (вҶ‘n*((R2 ПҒ Пғ).toReal + ОөвӮҖ + Оө2))) вҖў (Пғ'' ПҒ Оө m Пғ n).M}

  have hPcomm Оө2 n : Commute (P1 Оө2 n).toMat (P2 Оө2 n).toMat := by
    simp only [HermitianMat.proj_le, HermitianMat.cfc_toMat, P1, P2]
    apply IsSelfAdjoint.commute_cfc
    В· apply HermitianMat.H
    symm
    apply IsSelfAdjoint.commute_cfc
    В· apply HermitianMat.H
    simp only [AddSubgroupClass.coe_sub, MState.toMat_M, selfAdjoint.val_smul]
    suffices h : Commute (в„° n (ПҒвҠ—^S[n])).m (Пғ'' ПҒ Оө m Пғ n).m by
      apply Commute.sub_left
      В· exact (Commute.refl _).sub_right (h.smul_right _)
      В· exact (h.symm.sub_right ((Commute.refl _).smul_right _)).smul_left _
    exact pinching_commutes (ПҒвҠ—^S[n]) (Пғ'' ПҒ Оө m Пғ n)

  let E1 := 1 - P1 -- (S78)
  let E2 := P1 - P2 -- (S79)
  let E3 := P2 -- (S80)

  have Esum : E1 + E2 + E3 = 1 := by
    unfold E1 E2 E3
    abel

  have hE1proj Оө2 n : E1 Оө2 n = {(в„° n (ПҒвҠ—^S[n])).M <вӮҡ (Real.exp (вҶ‘n*((R1 ПҒ Оө).toReal + Оө2))) вҖў (Пғ'' ПҒ Оө m Пғ n).M} := by
    dsimp [E1, P1]
    rw [sub_eq_iff_eq_add]
    simp only [HermitianMat.proj_le_add_lt]

  have hE2leProj Оө2 n : E2 Оө2 n вүӨ {(в„° n (ПҒвҠ—^S[n])).M <вӮҡ (Real.exp (вҶ‘n*((R2 ПҒ Пғ).toReal + ОөвӮҖ + Оө2))) вҖў (Пғ'' ПҒ Оө m Пғ n).M} := by
    dsimp [E2, P1, P2]
    rw [sub_le_iff_le_add]
    simp only [HermitianMat.proj_le_add_lt]
    exact HermitianMat.proj_le_le_one _ _

  -- (S83)
  let c' Оө2 n := (ПғвӮҒ_c i n + (ПғвӮҒ_c i n) / n) вҠ” ((R2 ПҒ Пғ).toReal + ОөвӮҖ + Оө2)

  have hc' (Оө2 : в„• вҶ’ в„қвүҘ0) (hОө2 : вҲҖ n, Оө2 n < 1) :
      вҲғ (C : в„қвүҘ0), вҲҖб¶  (n : в„•) in Filter.atTop, c' (Оө2 n) n вүӨ C := by
    apply c'_bounded hОө2 _ (ПғвӮҒ_c_pos i)

  -- (S84)
  have hПғ'' Оө2 n : Real.exp (-n * c' Оө2 n) вҖў 1 вүӨ (Пғ'' ПҒ Оө m Пғ n).M := by
    rcases n.eq_zero_or_pos with rfl | hn
    В· have _ : Unique (H (i ^ 0)) := by
        rw [spacePow_zero]
        infer_instance
      apply le_of_eq
      simp [Unique.eq_default (Пғ'' ПҒ Оө m Пғ 0)]
    calc
      (Пғ'' ПҒ Оө m Пғ n).M вүҘ Real.exp (- ПғвӮҒ_c i n) вҖў (Пғ' ПҒ Оө m Пғ n).M := Пғ'_le_Пғ'' ПҒ Оө m Пғ n
      _ вүҘ (Real.exp (- ПғвӮҒ_c i n) * (1 / 3)) вҖў ((ПғвӮҒ i)вҠ—^S[n]).M := by
        grw [вҶҗ hПғвӮҒ_le_Пғ' ПҒ Оө m Пғ n, smul_smul]
      _ вүҘ (Real.exp (- ПғвӮҒ_c i n) * (1 / 3)) вҖў ((iInf ((ПғвӮҒ i)вҠ—^S[n]).M.H.eigenvalues) вҖў 1) := by
        apply smul_le_smul_of_nonneg_left
        В· exact ((ПғвӮҒ i)вҠ—^S[n]).M.H.iInf_eigenvalues_smul_one_le
        В· positivity
      _ = (Real.exp (- ПғвӮҒ_c i n) * (1 / 3) * (ПғвӮҒ_mineig i)^n) вҖў 1 := by
        dsimp [ПғвӮҒ_mineig, iInf]
        rw [вҶҗ Matrix.IsHermitian.spectrum_real_eq_range_eigenvalues]
        rw [вҶҗ Matrix.IsHermitian.spectrum_real_eq_range_eigenvalues]
        rw [MState.toMat_M, sInf_spectrum_spacePow (ПғвӮҒ i) n, MState.toMat_M, smul_smul]
      _ = Real.exp (- n * (ПғвӮҒ_c i n + (ПғвӮҒ_c i n) / n)) вҖў 1 := by
        rw [ПғвӮҒ_c_identity i hn]
      _ вүҘ Real.exp (-n * c' Оө2 n) вҖў 1 := by
        apply smul_le_smul_of_nonneg_right
        В· apply Real.exp_le_exp_of_le
          simp only [neg_mul, neg_le_neg_iff]
          apply mul_le_mul_of_nonneg_left _ (by positivity)
          dsimp [c']
          exact le_sup_left
        В· exact zero_le_one

  have hE3commв„° Оө2 n : Commute (E3 Оө2 n).toMat ((в„° n (ПҒвҠ—^S[n])).M.log.toMat) := by
    unfold E3 P2
    rw [HermitianMat.proj_le_def]
    apply HermitianMat.cfc_commute
    apply Commute.sub_left
    В· simp only [HermitianMat.val_eq_coe, MState.toMat_M, Commute.refl]
    В· apply Commute.smul_left
      apply Commute.symm
      exact pinching_commutes (ПҒвҠ—^S[n]) (Пғ'' ПҒ Оө m Пғ n)

  -- (S88)
  have hDleq Оө2 n (hОө2 : 0 < Оө2) (hn : 0 < n) : (рқҗғ(в„° n (ПҒвҠ—^S[n])вҖ–Пғ'' ПҒ Оө m Пғ n) / n : в„қвүҘ0вҲһ) вүӨ  ((R1 ПҒ Оө) + .ofReal Оө2) +
        .ofReal ((P1 Оө2 n).inner (в„° n (ПҒвҠ—^S[n]))) * ((R2 ПҒ Пғ + .ofReal ОөвӮҖ + .ofReal Оө2) - (R1 ПҒ Оө + .ofReal Оө2)) +
        .ofReal ((P2 Оө2 n).inner (в„° n (ПҒвҠ—^S[n]))) * (.ofReal (c' Оө2 n) - (R2 ПҒ Пғ + .ofReal ОөвӮҖ + .ofReal Оө2)) := by
    -- see (S81) for comments on why that statement had to be changed
    -- (S85)
    -- (first inequality should have $\sigma_n''$ instead of
    -- $\tilde{\sigma}_n''$; corrected in v4, where $\tilde{\sigma}_n'$ takes
    -- the place of $\sigma_n''$) in this and other steps
    have hE3leq : (1/n : в„қ) вҖў (E3 Оө2 n).toMat * ((в„° n (ПҒвҠ—^S[n])).M.log.toMat - (Пғ'' ПҒ Оө m Пғ n).M.log.toMat) вүӨ (c' Оө2 n) вҖў (E3 Оө2 n).toMat := by
      calc
      (1/n : в„қ) вҖў (E3 Оө2 n).toMat * ((в„° n (ПҒвҠ—^S[n])).M.log.toMat - (Пғ'' ПҒ Оө m Пғ n).M.log.toMat) вүӨ (1/n : в„қ) вҖў (E3 Оө2 n).toMat * (- (Пғ'' ПҒ Оө m Пғ n).M.log.toMat) := by
        -- first inequality of (S85)
        have hв„°ПҒlognonpos : 0 вүӨ -(в„° n (ПҒвҠ—^S[n])).M.log.toMat := by
          -- log of state is non-positive
          simp only [HermitianMat.log]
          rw [вҶҗ AddSubgroup.coe_neg _, вҶҗ HermitianMat.cfc_neg (в„° n (ПҒвҠ—^S[n])).M]
          change (HermitianMat.toMat 0) вүӨ _
          rw [Subtype.coe_le_coe, HermitianMat.zero_le_cfc (в„° n (ПҒвҠ—^S[n])).M (-Real.log)]
          intro i
          simp
          apply Real.log_nonpos
          В· apply MState.eigenvalue_nonneg _
          В· apply MState.eigenvalue_le_one
        rw [вҶҗ sub_nonneg, вҶҗ mul_sub_left_distrib]
        conv =>
          rhs
          congr; rfl
          rw [вҶҗ sub_add (-(Пғ'' ПҒ Оө m Пғ n).M.log.toMat) ((в„° n (ПҒвҠ—^S[n])).M.log.toMat) ((Пғ'' ПҒ Оө m Пғ n).M.log.toMat)]
          rw [add_comm_sub]
          rw [вҶҗ add_sub_assoc]
          simp [sub_self (Пғ'' ПҒ Оө m Пғ n).M.log.toMat]
        simp only [Algebra.smul_mul_assoc, one_div]
        have hE3в„°nonneg : 0 вүӨ (E3 Оө2 n).toMat * -(в„° n (ПҒвҠ—^S[n])).M.log.toMat := by
          apply Commute.mul_nonneg _ hв„°ПҒlognonpos (Commute.neg_right (hE3commв„° Оө2 n))
          apply HermitianMat.proj_le_nonneg
        apply smul_nonneg (inv_nonneg_of_nonneg (Nat.cast_nonneg' n)) hE3в„°nonneg
      _ вүӨ (1/n : в„қ) вҖў (E3 Оө2 n).toMat * (- (Real.exp (-n * c' Оө2 n) вҖў (1 : HermitianMat (H (i ^ n)) в„Ӯ)).log.toMat) := by
        -- intermediate step in 2nd ineq of S85
        simp only [mul_neg, neg_mul, neg_le_neg_iff]
        have h1logleq : (Real.exp (-(n * c' Оө2 n)) вҖў 1 : HermitianMat (H (i ^ n)) в„Ӯ).log.toMat вүӨ ((Пғ'' ПҒ Оө m Пғ n).M).log.toMat := by
          -- apply hПғ'' Оө2 n to log by monotonicity
          rw [Subtype.coe_le_coe]
          have h_comm : Commute ((Real.exp _ вҖў 1 : HermitianMat _ в„Ӯ).toMat) _ :=
            Commute.smul_left (Commute.one_left (Пғ'' ПҒ Оө m Пғ n).M.toMat) (Real.exp (-(n * c' Оө2 n)))
          exact HermitianMat.log_le_log_of_commute h_comm (by simpa using hПғ'' Оө2 n)
            (Matrix.PosDef.smul Matrix.PosDef.one (Real.exp_pos (-(n * c' Оө2 n))))
        rw [вҶҗ sub_nonneg] at h1logleq
        rw [вҶҗ sub_nonneg, вҶҗ mul_sub_left_distrib]
        simp only [one_div, Algebra.smul_mul_assoc]
        have hE3commlog : Commute (E3 Оө2 n).toMat ((Пғ'' ПҒ Оө m Пғ n).M.log.toMat - (Real.exp (-(n * c' Оө2 n)) вҖў 1 : HermitianMat _ в„Ӯ).log.toMat) := by
          -- projector commutes with logs
          apply Commute.sub_right
          В· -- prove Commute (E3 _) (Пғ'' _).log
            unfold E3 P2
            rw [HermitianMat.proj_le_def]
            apply HermitianMat.cfc_commute
            apply Commute.sub_left
            В· exact pinching_commutes (ПҒвҠ—^S[n]) (Пғ'' ПҒ Оө m Пғ n)
            В· apply Commute.smul_left
              В· rfl
          В· -- prove `Commute (E3 _) (_ 1).log`
            conv_rhs =>
              simp only [
                HermitianMat.log_smul (1 : HermitianMat _ в„Ӯ) (Real.exp _),
                Real.log_exp, neg_smul, HermitianMat.log_one,
                add_zero, NegMemClass.coe_neg,
                HermitianMat.val_eq_coe, selfAdjoint.val_smul,
                selfAdjoint.val_one
                ]
            simp only [Commute.neg_right_iff, Commute.smul_right (Commute.one_right _) _]
        apply smul_nonneg (inv_nonneg_of_nonneg (Nat.cast_nonneg' n))
        apply Commute.mul_nonneg _ h1logleq hE3commlog
        apply HermitianMat.proj_le_nonneg
      _ = (c' Оө2 n) вҖў (E3 Оө2 n).toMat := by
        simp [HermitianMat.log_smul, smul_smul]
        field_simp
    --Linearly combine S81, S82, S85:
    calc
      рқҗғ(в„° n (ПҒвҠ—^S[n])вҖ–Пғ'' ПҒ Оө m Пғ n) / (n : ENNReal) вүӨ
        ENNReal.ofReal (((в„° n (ПҒвҠ—^S[n])).M.inner (((R1 ПҒ Оө).toReal + Оө2) вҖў (E1 Оө2 n)))
        + ((в„° n (ПҒвҠ—^S[n])).M.inner (((R2 ПҒ Пғ).toReal + ОөвӮҖ + Оө2) вҖў (E2 Оө2 n)))
        + ((в„° n (ПҒвҠ—^S[n])).M.inner ((c' Оө2 n) вҖў (E3 Оө2 n))))
      := by
        -- (S86) to (S88)
        unfold qRelativeEnt SandwichedRelRentropy
        simp only [вҶ“reduceIte]
        have Пғ''_pd := Пғ''_posdef ПҒ Оө m Пғ
        simp only [MState.toMat_M] at Пғ''_pd
        have hker : (Пғ'' ПҒ Оө m Пғ n).M.ker вүӨ (в„° n (ПҒвҠ—^S[n])).M.ker :=
          ker_le_ker_pinching_of_PosDef (ПҒвҠ—^S[n]) (Пғ'' ПҒ Оө m Пғ n) (Пғ''_pd n)
        simp only [hker, if_true]
        have hMulOne : (в„° n (ПҒвҠ—^S[n])).M.toMat * (1 : Matrix (H (i ^ n)) (H (i ^ n)) в„Ӯ) = (в„° n (ПҒвҠ—^S[n])).M.toMat := Matrix.mul_one (в„° n (ПҒвҠ—^S[n])).M.toMat
        have hOneMulCommute : Commute (1 : HermitianMat _ в„Ӯ).toMat (в„° n (ПҒвҠ—^S[n])).M.toMat := Commute.one_left (в„° n (ПҒвҠ—^S[n])).M.toMat
        have hOneIsOne : вҲҖ (Оө : в„қ) (n : в„•), (1 : в„қ вҶ’ в„• вҶ’ HermitianMat (H (i ^ n)) в„Ӯ) Оө n = (1 : HermitianMat (H (i ^ n)) в„Ӯ) := by
          intro Оө n; rfl
        /- convert Esum to the HermitianMat equality at point (Оө2, n) -/
        have Esum' : (E1 Оө2 n).toMat + (E2 Оө2 n).toMat + (E3 Оө2 n).toMat = 1 :=
          congrArg HermitianMat.toMat (congrFun (congrFun Esum Оө2) n)
        conv =>
          enter [1, 1, 1, 1]
          unfold HermitianMat.inner
          rw [вҶҗ hMulOne]
          rw [вҶҗ Esum']
        -- (S87)
        /- Use hE1leq, hE2leq, hE3leq -/

        /-the next two `have`s are duplicates-/
        -- TODO streamline what's below
        /-it should transform a HermitianMat inequality into a reals inequality with HermitianMat.inner_mono,
        the difficulty here is that inner_mono relies on the entries being HermitianMat, but the inequalities are expressed as matrices-/
        have hE2comm : Commute (E2 Оө2 n).toMat (((в„° n (ПҒвҠ—^S[n])).M.log - (Пғ'' ПҒ Оө m Пғ n).M.log).toMat) := by
        -- TODO this needs to be extracted from here, it's badly redundant
          apply Commute.sub_right
          В· unfold E2 P1 P2
            simp
            rw [HermitianMat.proj_le_def, HermitianMat.proj_le_def]
            apply Commute.sub_left
            В· apply HermitianMat.cfc_commute
              apply Commute.sub_left
              В· rfl
              В· simp
                apply Commute.symm
                exact pinching_commutes (ПҒвҠ—^S[n]) (Пғ'' ПҒ Оө m Пғ n)
            В· apply HermitianMat.cfc_commute
              apply Commute.sub_left
              В· rfl
              В· simp
                apply Commute.symm
                exact pinching_commutes (ПҒвҠ—^S[n]) (Пғ'' ПҒ Оө m Пғ n)
          В· unfold E2 P1 P2
            simp
            rw [HermitianMat.proj_le_def, HermitianMat.proj_le_def]
            apply Commute.sub_left
            В· apply HermitianMat.cfc_commute
              apply Commute.sub_left
              В· exact pinching_commutes (ПҒвҠ—^S[n]) (Пғ'' ПҒ Оө m Пғ n)
              В· simp
            В· apply HermitianMat.cfc_commute
              apply Commute.sub_left
              В· exact pinching_commutes (ПҒвҠ—^S[n]) (Пғ'' ПҒ Оө m Пғ n)
              В· simp
        have hE2leqInner : (n : в„қ)вҒ»В№ * ((в„° n (ПҒвҠ—^S[n])).M.toMat * (E2 Оө2 n).toMat * ((в„° n (ПҒвҠ—^S[n])).M.log.toMat - (Пғ'' ПҒ Оө m Пғ n).M.log.toMat)).trace.re вүӨ ((R2 ПҒ Пғ).toReal + ОөвӮҖ + Оө2) * ((в„° n (ПҒвҠ—^S[n])).M).inner (E2 Оө2 n) := by
          open HermMul in
          -- (S82) -- see (S81) for comments
          have hE2leq Оө2 (n : в„•) (hОө2 : 0 < Оө2) : (1/n : в„қ) вҖў (E2 Оө2 n).toMat * ((в„° n (ПҒвҠ—^S[n])).M.log.toMat - (Пғ'' ПҒ Оө m Пғ n).M.log.toMat) вүӨ ((R2 ПҒ Пғ).toReal + ОөвӮҖ + Оө2) вҖў (E2 Оө2 n).toMat := by
            refine rexp_mul_smul_proj_lt_mul_sub_le_mul_sub'
              (pinching_commutes (ПҒвҠ—^S[n]) (Пғ'' ПҒ Оө m Пғ n)) ?_ (Пғ''_posdef ПҒ Оө m Пғ n) rfl
            rw [вҶҗ HermitianMat.zero_le_iff]
            apply MState.zero_le
          simp at hE2leq
          rw [вҶҗ Complex.re_ofReal_mul (вҶ‘n)вҒ»В№, вҶҗ smul_eq_mul, вҶҗ Matrix.trace_smul]
          rw [вҶҗ RCLike.re_to_complex]
          conv =>
            enter [1, 2]
            rw [mul_assoc]
            enter [1, 2, 2]
            norm_cast
            rw [вҶҗ HermitianMat.symmMul_of_commute hE2comm]
          conv at hE2leq =>
            enter [Оө2, n, hОө2, 1, 2, 2]
            norm_cast
          specialize hE2leq Оө2 n hОө2
          rw [вҶҗ HermitianMat.symmMul_of_commute hE2comm] at hE2leq
          conv_lhs at hE2leq =>
            change (Complex.ofReal (_ : в„қ)) вҖў _
            rw [HermitianMat.smul_toMat (HermitianMat.symmMul _ _) (n : в„қ)вҒ»В№]
          conv_rhs at hE2leq =>
            change (Complex.ofReal (_ : в„қ)) вҖў _
            rw [HermitianMat.smul_toMat (E2 Оө2 n) _]
          rw [вҶҗ Matrix.mul_smul (в„° n (ПҒвҠ—^S[n])).M.toMat (Complex.ofReal (n : в„қ)вҒ»В№) (HermitianMat.symmMul _ _).toMat]
          simp only [HermitianMat.smul_toMat]
          rw [вҶҗ HermitianMat.inner_eq_re_trace (в„° n (ПҒвҠ—^S[n])).M ((n : в„қ)вҒ»В№ вҖў (HermitianMat.symmMul _ _))]
          rw [вҶҗ HermitianMat.inner_smul]
          exact ((HermitianMat.inner_mono ((в„° n (ПҒвҠ—^S[n]))).zero_le) hE2leq)
        simp at hE3leq
        /-this and the `have` above are duplicates-/
        have hE3comm : Commute (E3 Оө2 n).toMat (((в„° n (ПҒвҠ—^S[n])).M.log - (Пғ'' ПҒ Оө m Пғ n).M.log).toMat) := by
          apply Commute.sub_right
          В· simp [(hE3commв„° Оө2 n)]
          В· unfold E3 P2
            simp
            rw [HermitianMat.proj_le_def]
            apply HermitianMat.cfc_commute
            apply Commute.sub_left
            В· exact pinching_commutes (ПҒвҠ—^S[n]) (Пғ'' ПҒ Оө m Пғ n)
            В· simp
        /- hE3commв„° -/
        have hE3leqInner : (n : в„қ)вҒ»В№ * ((в„° n (ПҒвҠ—^S[n])).M.toMat * (E3 Оө2 n).toMat * ((в„° n (ПҒвҠ—^S[n])).M.log.toMat - (Пғ'' ПҒ Оө m Пғ n).M.log.toMat)).trace.re вүӨ (c' Оө2 n) * ((в„° n (ПҒвҠ—^S[n])).M).inner (E3 Оө2 n) := by
          open HermMul in
          rw [вҶҗ Complex.re_ofReal_mul (вҶ‘n)вҒ»В№ _, вҶҗ smul_eq_mul, вҶҗ Matrix.trace_smul]
          rw [вҶҗ RCLike.re_to_complex]
          conv =>
            enter [1, 2]
            rw [mul_assoc]
            enter [1, 2, 2, 2]
            norm_cast
          conv =>
            enter [1, 2, 1, 2, 2]
            rw [вҶҗ HermitianMat.symmMul_of_commute hE3comm]
          conv at hE3leq =>
            enter [1, 2, 2]
            norm_cast
          rw [вҶҗ HermitianMat.symmMul_of_commute hE3comm] at hE3leq
          conv at hE3leq =>
            lhs
            change (Complex.ofReal (_ : в„қ)) вҖў _
            rw [HermitianMat.smul_toMat (HermitianMat.symmMul _ _) (n : в„қ)вҒ»В№]
          conv at hE3leq =>
            rhs
            change (Complex.ofReal (_ : в„қ)) вҖў _
            rw [HermitianMat.smul_toMat (E3 Оө2 n) _]
          rw [вҶҗ Matrix.mul_smul (в„° n (ПҒвҠ—^S[n])).M.toMat (Complex.ofReal (n : в„қ)вҒ»В№) (HermitianMat.symmMul _ _).toMat]
          simp only [HermitianMat.smul_toMat]
          rw [вҶҗ HermitianMat.inner_eq_re_trace (в„° n (ПҒвҠ—^S[n])).M ((n : в„қ)вҒ»В№ вҖў (HermitianMat.symmMul _ _))]
          rw [вҶҗ HermitianMat.inner_smul]
          exact ((HermitianMat.inner_mono ((в„° n (ПҒвҠ—^S[n]))).zero_le) hE3leq)
        simp only [IsMaximalSelfAdjoint.RCLike_selfadjMap, MState.toMat_M,
          AddSubgroupClass.coe_sub, HermitianMat.val_eq_coe,
          RCLike.re_to_complex,
          HermitianMat.inner_smul, ge_iff_le]
        conv =>
          enter [1, 1, 1, 1]
          rw [mul_add, mul_add, add_mul, add_mul, trace_add, trace_add]
        simp [вҶҗ ENNReal.ofReal_coe_nnreal, NNReal.toReal]
        rw [вҶҗ ENNReal.ofReal_natCast, вҶҗ ENNReal.ofReal_div_of_pos (by simp [hn]), div_eq_inv_mul]
        rw [ENNReal.ofReal_le_ofReal_iff']
        В· left
          rw [mul_add, mul_add]
          apply add_le_add_three
          В· unfold HermitianMat.inner
            simp

            -- (S81)
            /- A literal translation of the paper would read:
                (1/n : в„қ) вҖў (E1 Оө2 n).toMat * ((в„° n (ПҒвҠ—^S[n])).M.log.toMat - (Пғ'' n).M.log.toMat) вүӨ ((R1 ПҒ Оө).toReal + Оө2) вҖў (E1 Оө2 n).toMat
            But this is simply not true! Because what happens when `в„° n (ПҒвҠ—^S[n])` has a zero eigenvalue, which
            it can? Then (S81) is an inequality of operators where the LHS has an operator with a "negative
            infinity" eigenvalue, intuitively. This isn't something very well defined, certainly not supported
            in our definitions. This only becomes mathematically meaningful when we see how it's used later, in
            (S88): both sides are traced against `в„° n (ПҒвҠ—^S[n])`, so that the 0 eigenvalues becomes irrelevant. This
            is the version we state and prove, then.

            Luckily, (S82) and (S85) are correct as written (in a particular interpretation), because
            there the problematic subspaces are indeed projected out by the EвӮӮ and EвӮғ operators.
            -/
            have hE1leq Оө2 (n : в„•) (hОө2 : 0 < Оө2) :
                (в„° n (ПҒвҠ—^S[n])).M.inner (((1 / (n : в„қ)) вҖў (E1 Оө2 n)).symmMul
                  ((((pinching_map (Пғ'' ПҒ Оө m Пғ n)) (ПҒвҠ—^S[n])).M).log - ((Пғ'' ПҒ Оө m Пғ n).M).log : HermitianMat _ в„Ӯ)) вүӨ
                  (в„° n (ПҒвҠ—^S[n])).M.inner (((R1 ПҒ Оө).toReal + Оө2) вҖў (E1 Оө2 n)) := by
              refine rexp_mul_smul_proj_lt_mul_sub_le_mul_sub
                (pinching_commutes (ПҒвҠ—^S[n]) (Пғ'' ПҒ Оө m Пғ n)) (by positivity) ?_ (Пғ''_posdef ПҒ Оө m Пғ n) rfl
              rw [вҶҗ HermitianMat.zero_le_iff]
              apply MState.zero_le

            unfold HermitianMat.inner at hE1leq
            conv at hE1leq =>
              enter [Оө2, n, hОө2, 1]
              rw [HermitianMat.symmMul_of_commute (commute_aux n (E := E1 Оө2 n) (pinching_commutes (ПҒвҠ—^S[n]) (Пғ'' ПҒ Оө m Пғ n)) rfl)]
            simp at hE1leq
            conv at hE1leq =>
              intro Оө2 n hОө2
              rw [вҶҗ mul_assoc]
              pattern (pinching_map (Пғ'' ПҒ Оө m Пғ n))
              change в„° n
            apply (hE1leq Оө2 n hОө2)
          В· apply hE2leqInner
          В· apply hE3leqInner
      _ = _ := by
        unfold E1 E2 E3
        simp [HermitianMat.inner_left_sub]
        ring_nf
        repeat rw [ENNReal.ofReal_add] -- 46 goals !!! --RSS
